le' font-size='11' fill='#8888aa'>190</text><text x='-8' y='272.0' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='#8888aa'>50</text><text x='-8' y='212.4' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='#8888aa'>60</text><text x='-8' y='152.9' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='#8888aa'>70</text><text x='-8' y='93.3' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='#8888aa'>80</text><text x='-8' y='33.8' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='#8888aa'>90</text><circle cx='513' cy='6'  r='6' fill='#7c3aed' fill-opacity='0.8'/><text x='525' y='11' font-size='12' fill='#8888aa'>Group A</text><circle cx='513' cy='28' r='6' fill='#06b6d4' fill-opacity='0.8'/><text x='525' y='33' font-size='12' fill='#8888aa'>Group B</text><line x1='505' y1='52' x2='521' y2='52' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2' stroke-dasharray='5,2'/><text x='525' y='56' font-size='12' fill='#8888aa'>Trend</text><text x='505' y='76' font-size='11' fill='#8888aa'>R²=0.089</text><text x='505' y='93' font-size='11' fill='#8888aa'>m=0.33</text> <text text-anchor='middle' fill='#8888aa' font-size='11' transform='translate(-44,134) rotate(-90)'>Weight (kg)</text> <text x='247.5' y='306' text-anchor='middle' font-size='11' fill='#8888aa'>Height (cm)</text> </g> </svg>\n",
